  "riddle": "1. In the realm of South Korean dramas, there exists an actress whose debut marked the beginning of a remarkable journey. Discover the year she first graced our screens.\n\n2. To continue, take the digits of that year you uncovered and sum them together. What number do you arrive at?\n\n3. From a name shared by many, how many individuals with this famous surname were recorded in South Korea's 2015 census?\n\n4. Seek the entertainment agency known for nurturing stars, where you can find trades under a particular ticker — what is that ticker?\n\n5. Now, examine the first letter of that ticker; what position does it occupy in the alphabet (A=1, B=2, and so on)?\n\n6. Journey to the page of the network that brings tales from this agency to the screen. Which country is home to this network?\n\n7. Reflecting on the nation you just identified, how many people reside there according to the latest statistics?\n\n8. Next, how vast is this land, measured in square kilometers?\n\n9. Add the population you calculated in clue 7 to the area you just determined from clue 8. What number does this calculation yield?\n\n10. For further verification, revisit the area of this same country in square kilometers. \n\n11. Delve into a series that tells the gripping stories of its people — how many seasons does this Turkish drama comprise?\n\n12. This historic district in your search has its own coordinates marked; what are those precise points that define its location?\n\n13. Ascend to the heights of this locale — how far above sea level does it stand?\n\n14. Count the places of worship nearby this vibrant area; how many temples can you uncover?\n\n15. Combine the elevation from clue 13 with the temple count from clue 14. What new total do you find?\n\n16. Approach a contemporary stage where creative voices speak. How many hospitals lie in proximity to the precise coordinates you've encountered?\n\n17. As your quest comes to an end, compute the result of taking the absolute difference between 2005 and the sum from clue 15, followed by finding its remainder after division by 10. This single digit holds the final answer of your journey—what is it?",
